title: Weekend Bite: Risk-on or Risk-off? That is the Question w/ Michael Gayed, CFA.
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: This week we're joined by Michael A. Gayed, CFA., Founder of The Lead-Lag Report. We discuss the macro environment, is it the perfect time to go risk-on, and why Michael doesn't see cash as an asset class.
